Class UMLMessageArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.purdue.cs59000.umltranslator.message.UMLMessageArgument

  • public class UMLMessageArgument
extends java.lang.Object
    A UMLMessageArgument is similar to a method parameter. Every method parameter has a name, a data type, an initial value, and a flag that determines whether or not the number of arguments is specified (in Java this is ellipsis (â€¦) ).
